 design, their rich texture and mouth-watering flavor always comes first. It\u2019s our goal to create desserts that both look <em>and<\/em> taste amazing. What\u2019s more \u2014 we use only buttercream frosting for all of our cake designs. This means every mouthful is delicious, and you\u2019ll never have to choose between a perfectly smooth fondant-style finish or a frosting that you\u2019ll actually enjoy eating.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-rowlayout alignnone\"><div id=\"kt-layout-id_69de90-3d\" class=\"kt-row-layout-inner kt-layout-id_69de90-3d\"><div class=\"kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-3-columns kt-gutter-default kt-v-gutter-default kt-row-valign-top kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-inherit kt-m-colapse-left-to-right kt-mobile-layout-row\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-1 kadence-column_c584f3-a2\"><div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\"><style id=\"kb-advancedbtn_96cf41-13\">.kt-btns_96cf41-13 .kt-btn-wrap-0{margin-right:5px;}.rtl .kt-btns_96cf41-13 .kt-btn-wrap-0{margin-left:5px;margin-right:0px;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_96cf41-13 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button{color:#555555;border-color:#555555;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_96cf41-13 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:hover, .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_96cf41-13 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:focus{color:#ffffff;border-color:#444444;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_96cf41-13 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button::before{display:none;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_96cf41-13 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:hover, .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_96cf41-13 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:focus{background:#444444;}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn kt-btn-align-center kt-btn-tablet-align-inherit kt-btn-mobile-align-inherit kt-btns-wrap kt-btns_96cf41-13\"><div class=\"kt-btn-wrap kt-btn-wrap-0\"><a class=\"kt-button button kt-btn-0-action kt-btn-size-standard kt-btn-style-basic kt-btn-svg-show-always kt-btn-has-text-true kt-btn-has-svg-false\" href=\"\/weddings\"><span class=\"kt-btn-inner-text\">WEDDING CAKES<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-2 kadence-column_cfe866-02\"><div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\"><style id=\"kb-advancedbtn_2dc6e8-67\">.kt-btns_2dc6e8-67 .kt-btn-wrap-0{margin-right:5px;}.rtl .kt-btns_2dc6e8-67 .kt-btn-wrap-0{margin-left:5px;margin-right:0px;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_2dc6e8-67 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button{color:#555555;border-color:#555555;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_2dc6e8-67 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:hover, .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_2dc6e8-67 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:focus{color:#ffffff;border-color:#444444;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_2dc6e8-67 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button::before{display:none;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_2dc6e8-67 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:hover, .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_2dc6e8-67 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:focus{background:#444444;}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn kt-btn-align-center kt-btn-tablet-align-inherit kt-btn-mobile-align-inherit kt-btns-wrap kt-btns_2dc6e8-67\"><div class=\"kt-btn-wrap kt-btn-wrap-0\"><a class=\"kt-button button kt-btn-0-action kt-btn-size-standard kt-btn-style-basic kt-btn-svg-show-always kt-btn-has-text-true kt-btn-has-svg-false\" href=\"\/other-celebrations\"><span class=\"kt-btn-inner-text\">OTHER CELEBRATIONS<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-3 kadence-column_14ed43-90\"><div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\"><style id=\"kb-advancedbtn_0de467-28\">.kt-btns_0de467-28 .kt-btn-wrap-0{margin-right:5px;}.rtl .kt-btns_0de467-28 .kt-btn-wrap-0{margin-left:5px;margin-right:0px;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_0de467-28 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button{color:#555555;border-color:#555555;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_0de467-28 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:hover, .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns_0de467-28 .kt-btn-wrap