, every custom dessert from Craig\u2019s Cake Shop is baked and decorated to perfection by hearts and hands with years of experience and a heap of enthusiasm. We can\u2019t say enough about the phenomenal people who put their whole selves into our creations day in and day out.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Interested in becoming a part of the Craig\u2019s family? Check out our open positions on our <a href=\"\/careers\">careers<\/a> page.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-rowlayout alignfull footer-hat bg-full cupcakes\"><div id=\"kt-layout-id_d4a695-6d\" class=\"kt-row-layout-inner  kt-layout-id_d4a695-6d\"><div class=\"kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-2-columns kt-gutter-default kt-v-gutter-default kt-row-valign-middle kt-row-layout-right-golden kt-tab-layout-row kt-m-colapse-left-to-right kt-mobile-layout-row\"><style id=\"kb-column_f5d1d3-12\">.kadence-column_f5d1d3-12 > .kt-inside-inner-col{border-color:#e2b9e7;}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-1 kadence-column_f5d1d3-12\"><div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\">\n<h2>Follow Us<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Stay up to date on our latest custom cake creations and company news.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"social-icons\">\n      <a href=\"https:\/\/facebook.com\/craigscakeshop\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/icon_fb@2x.png\" alt=\"Faceookb\">\n        \n        <span>Facebook<\/span>\n      <\/a>\n      <a href=\"https:\/\/instagram.com\/craigscakeshop\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/icon_instagram@2x.png\" alt=\"Instagram\">\n        \n        <span>Instagram<\/span>\n      <\/a>\n      <a href=\"https:\/\/pin.it\/ifyd57ggosrth6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/icon_pinterest@2x.png\" alt=\"Pinterest\">\n        \n        <span>Pinterest<\/span>